WEBVTT

00:02:29.962 --> 00:02:32.069
wanagundua unapenda kuvaa magauni meusi,

00:02:32.069 --> 00:02:34.505
hivyo mtu kwenye duka anakuja na kusema,

00:02:34.505 --> 00:02:36.805
"Vipi, tuna magauni meusi matano

00:02:36.805 --> 00:02:40.038
ambayo yangekupendeza sana wewe."

00:02:40.038 --> 00:02:42.158
Basi kama je Andy alikosea?

00:02:42.158 --> 00:02:43.428
Hii hapa kanuni ya Andy.

00:02:43.428 --> 00:02:45.272
[Mbeleni, kila mtu atakua maarufu dakika 15.]

00:02:45.272 --> 00:02:46.538
Je kama tukigeuza hili?

00:02:46.538 --> 00:02:51.059
Je kama utakua haujulikani kwa
dakika 15 tu? (Kicheko)

00:02:51.059 --> 00:02:54.075
Basi, tena, kwa sababu ya michoro ya
elektroniki,

00:02:54.075 --> 00:02:58.736
labda nyie wote na sisi wote tuko karibu
sana na ukosefu wa maadili,

00:02:58.736 --> 00:03:00.314
kwa sababu hii michoro itaishi